data.description: Adorable 3-bedroom 1 bathroom home with a large bonus room. Centrally located with views of the Sonoma Mtns and town from the large and private backyard.  The kitchen has granite countertops and newer cabinets.  This immaculate turnkey home is ready for you to make it your own.
